quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  34,49,"Qul jaa alhaqqu wamayubdi-o albatilu wama yuAAeed"
  34,50,"Qul in dalaltu fa-innama adilluAAala nafsee wa-ini ihtadaytu fabima yooheeilayya rabbee innahu sameeAAun qareeb"
  34,51,"Walaw tara ith faziAAoo falafawta waokhithoo min makanin qareeb"
  34,52,"Waqaloo amanna bihiwaanna lahumu attanawushu min makaninbaAAeed"
  34,53,"Waqad kafaroo bihi min qablu wayaqthifoonabilghaybi min makanin baAAeed"
  34,54,"Waheela baynahum wabayna mayashtahoona kama fuAAila bi-ashyaAAihim min qabluinnahum kanoo fee shakkin mureeb"
  35,1,"Alhamdu lillahi fatiri assamawatiwal-ardi jaAAili almala-ikatirusulan olee ajnihatin mathna wathulathawarubaAAa yazeedu fee alkhalqi ma yashaoinna Allaha AAala kulli shay-in qadeer"
  35,2,"Ma yaftahi Allahu linnasimin rahmatin fala mumsika laha wamayumsik fala mursila lahu min baAAdihi wahuwa alAAazeezu alhakeem"
  35,3,"Ya ayyuha annasuothkuroo niAAmata Allahi AAalaykum hal min khaliqinghayru Allahi yarzuqukum mina assama-i wal-ardila ilaha illa huwa faanna tu/fakoon"
